{"type":"message","id":"bef4a12a","parentId":"eaaa89ac","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:04:48.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n5n3h4yj2uwg_2","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\\n\\n[Subagent Task]: ## Task: Fix QLHV Auth UI — Login + Register Forms\\n\\n**Project:** AHV QLHV Frontend  \\n**Workspace:** /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Bugs Found\\n\\n**Bug #1 — Login form misleading UX:**\\nFile: `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx`\\n- Field \\\"Tên đăng nhập\\\" uses `Mail` icon (from lucide-react) which is misleading — users might think they should enter their email\\n- Fix: Change icon to `User` (already imported from lucide-react) and update placeholder text to clearly say \\\"Nhập tên đăng nhập\\\"\\n\\n**Bug #2 — Register form missing fields:**\\nFile: `src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx`\\n- Frontend sends only: `username, password, first_name, last_name, email, phone`\\n- Backend model requires `address` and `identity_card` as required fields\\n- Fix: Add two optional input fields for `address` and `identity_card` so users can fill them during registration, OR update the form to send default values\\n\\n**Note:** The backend fix (by senior-backend agent) will also provide defaults server-side. You can choose EITHER:\\n- (A) Add address + identity_card fields to the register form UI (better UX — user provides real data)\\n- (B) Just fix Bug #1 (login icon) and rely on backend defaults\\n\\nRecommendation: Option A is better UX. Add both fields with appropriate icons.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Fix #1: Login Page Icon Fix\\n\\nIn `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx`:\\n- Change `import { Mail, Lock, ChevronRight, User, AlertCircle } from 'lucide-react';` → keep `Mail` if needed for email field\\n- For the \\\"Tên đăng nhập\\\" input, use `User` icon instead of `Mail`\\n- Change placeholder from `placeholder=\\\"admin\\\"` to `placeholder=\\\"Nhập tên đăng nhập\\\"`\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Fix #2: Register Page — Add Missing Fields\\n\\nIn `src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx`, after the Email field (before Password field), add:\\n\\n```tsx\\n// Address field\\n<div className=\\\"space-y-1.5 relative group\\\">\\n  <label className=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest pl-1\\\">Địa chỉ</label>\\n  <div className=\\\"relative\\\">\\n    <MapPin className=\\\"absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-focus-within:text-primary transition-colors\\\" />\\n    <input \\n      type=\\\"text\\\" \\n      placeholder=\\\"123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP.HCM\\\" \\n      value={address}\\n      onChange={(e) => setAddress(e.target.value)}\\n      className=\\\"w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl font-medium outline-none focus:border-primary/20 focus:bg-white transition-all text-gray-900\\\"\\n    />\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n\\n// Identity Card field\\n<div className=\\\"space-y-1.5 relative group\\\">\\n  <label className=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest pl-1\\\">Số CCCD/CMND</label>\\n  <div className=\\\"relative\\\">\\n    <FileText className=\\\"absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-focus-within:text-primary transition-colors\\\" />\\n    <input \\n      type=\\\"text\\\" \\n      placeholder=\\\"079123456789\\\" \\n      value={identityCard}\\n      onChange={(e) => setIdentityCard(e.target.value)}\\n      className=\\\"w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl font-medium outline-none focus:border-primary/20 focus:bg-white transition-all text-gray-900\\\"\\n    />\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n```\\n\\nAdd state: `const [address, setAddress] = useState(''); const [identityCard, setIdentityCard] = useState('');`\\n\\nUpdate `handleSubmit` payload to include:\\n```typescript\\naddress,\\nidentity_card: identityCard,\\n```\\n\\nImport icons: `MapPin, FileText` from lucide-react\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Execution Steps\\n\\n1. Read current `login/page.tsx` and `register/page.tsx`\\n2. Apply Fix #1 (login icon)\\n3. Apply Fix #2 (register fields)  \\n4. Run `yarn lint` to verify\\n5. Commit with message: `fix(auth-ui): correct login icon and add address/identity_card fields to register form`\\n\\n### WORKING DIRECTORY\\n`/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.\\n…(truncated)…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1776045192649,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"74b86c90\",\n        \"seq\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-TroLy\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776045192695,\n      \"errorMessage\": \"500 {\\\"error\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\\\"}}\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"eaa796ee\",\n        \"seq\": 2\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-TroLy\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776045200502,\n      \"errorMessage\": \"500 {\\\"error\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\\\"}}\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"b35eee8c\",\n        \"seq\": 3\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [],\n      \"api\